Package: samba-configurator
Version: 1.0.7
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, samba, pkexec
Description: GTK4 application for managing Samba shared folders
 Samba Configurator is a user-friendly graphical application for managing
 Samba shared folders on Linux systems. It provides an intuitive
 interface to add, edit, and remove network shares with support
 for multiple languages.
 .
 Features include:
  - Add and remove Samba shares
  - Edit share properties (permissions, users, masks)
  - Support for guest access and read-only shares
  - Multi-language support based on system locale
